"5:112:12" : {s: 5, a: 112, w: 12, r: "", t: "عَلَيْنَا", l: "عَلَىٰ", lc: 1445, tl: "AAalayna", lb: "উপরে, থেকে, চেয়ে, ব্যাপারে",e: "to us", b: "আমাদের কাছে/আমাদের উপর/আমাদের জন্য", i: "atas kami", f: 51, rm: ""},
"5:112:13" : {s: 5, a: 112, w: 13, r: "ميد", t: "مَآئِدَةًۭ", l: "مَآئِدَة", lc: 2, tl: "māidatan", lb: "দস্তরখান, খাদ্য",e: "a table spread", b: "একটা খাঞ্চা", i: "makanan", f: 2, rm: "To be shaken, moved, agitated, spread, give food. It was/became in a state of motion or commotion. Was/Became agitated: in a state or violent motion or commotion; or violently agitated. Turn/Twist about. Become contorted and convulsed. Quivered, trembled. Confound, perplex, amazed. Inclining from side to side. Confer bestow benefit/s or favor/s."},
