"5:112:17" : {s: 5, a: 112, w: 17, r: "وقي", t: "ٱتَّقُوا۟", l: "ٱتَّقَىٰ", lc: 166, tl: "ittaqū", lb: "কোনো কিছুর ব্যাপারে অত্যন্ত সচেতন থাকা, আল্লাহর প্রতি সচেতন থাকা",e: "Fear", b: "তোমরা ভয় করো", i: "bertakwalah kamu", f: 14, rm: "to protect, save, preserve, ward off, guard against evil and calamity, be secure, take as a shield, regard the duty. muttaqii - one who guard against evil and against that which harms and injures and is regardful of his duty towards human beings and God."},
